============================================================================
Frieve Editor Version 3.00 Help
============================================================================

Thank you for downloading Frieve Editor.
Frieve Editor is a new kind of editor designed to help you organize your thoughts
and come up with original ideas.

To browse this help file, select the topic you want from Cards on the left side
of the screen.
You can also follow the links shown at the bottom of the screen to open related articles.
