----------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to Select Cards
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Click the Browser tab.
2. Click the card you want to select. To select multiple cards at the same time,
   hold down Ctrl while clicking cards.

Or,

1. Click the Browser tab.
2. Hold down Shift and drag over an empty area to define a selection range.
   Cards inside the range you drag out with the mouse are selected.

Or,

Click cards in the Cards list on the left side of the screen.
To select multiple cards, hold down Ctrl while clicking cards, drag over the
range you want to select, or select the first card in the range and then hold
down Shift while clicking the last card in the range.
