----------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to Sort Cards
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Choose a sort method from Edit menu -> Sort Card.
Title sorts cards by title.
Date Created sorts by creation order.
Date Edited sorts by the date the card was last edited.
Date Viewed sorts by the date the card was last selected.
Items marked Inverse sort in the reverse order.

Or,

1. Click the card you want to reorder in the Cards list on the left side of the screen.
2. Use the UpDown buttons at the upper right of the Cards list to move the card's
   position in the list.
