-
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to Scroll the Browser
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Click the Browser tab.
2. Check Auto Scroll at the upper right of the Browser tab.
   While Auto Scroll is checked, each time you select a card or link, the Browser
   scrolls automatically so that the selected card or link comes to the center of
   the screen.

Or,

1. Click the Browser tab.
2. Drag an empty area where there is no card.

Or,

1. Click the Browser tab.
2. Use the scroll bars on the right and bottom of the Browser screen.

Or,

1. Click the Browser tab.
2. Use the mouse wheel (without Ctrl) to scroll vertically.
   Hold Shift for horizontal panning (trackpad two-finger scroll).
35
Title: How to Zoom the Browser
