----------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to Change Text Size
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Choose Magnify or Reduce from View menu -> Font Size.

Or,

Press Ctrl+Shift+PageUp to enlarge or Ctrl+Shift+PageDown to reduce.

Or,

Hold down Ctrl+Shift and use the mouse wheel to change the font size.

To return the text size to its default value, choose Default from View menu -> Font Size, or press Ctrl+Shift+0.
