----------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to Open External Links Attached to Cards
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Click the Browser tab.
2. Hold down Ctrl and Shift while clicking the card whose external link you want to open.
   If the card has only one external link, it opens immediately.
3. If the card has multiple external links, click the link you want to open in the
   popup menu that appears.

Or,

1. Double-click the card whose external link you want to open in the Browser, or
   double-click it in the Card list on the left side of the screen. If that card is
   already selected, click the Editor tab to display the Editor.
2. Hold down Ctrl while clicking the line that contains the external link.
