----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Edit Menu
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Undo
  Cancels the most recent edit.

Redo
  Repeats the edit that was most recently undone.


Cut
  Copies the selected text to the clipboard and then deletes it.

Copy
  Copies the selected text to the clipboard.

Paste
  Pastes the clipboard text at the current position.

Delete
  Deletes the selected text.

Select All
  Selects all text.


Find
  Searches for a specified string.

Replace
  Replaces a specified string with another string.

Find Next
  Searches for the next occurrence of the specified string.

Find Previous
  Searches for the previous occurrence of the specified string.

Web Search
  Searches the web using the selected card title or selected text.


Sort Card
  Sorts cards by card name or date.

Barch Conversion
  All Cards Shape batch-converts all cards to the specified shape.
  All Links Shape batch-converts all links to the specified shape.
  All Links Direction reverses the direction of all links.


Label
  Opens the label editing dialog.

Link Label
  Opens the link label editing dialog.
