----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Insert Menu
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

New Card
  Creates a new card.

New Link
  Creates a new link from the selected card.

New Ext Link
  Inserts an external link (file name) into the selected card.

New Label
  Adds a new label to the selected card.

New Link Label
  Adds a new label to the selected link.


Link to All Cards with Designated Label
  Creates links from the current card to all cards that have the specified label.

New Card Links to All Cards with Designated Label
  Creates a new card linked to all cards that have the specified label.

Add Designated Label to All Destination Cards
  Adds the specified label to all destination cards.
