----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Animation Menu
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Random Flash
  Runs an animation that shows cards at random.

Random Map
  Runs an animation that shows a random card and then expands the display to cards
  linked from that card.

Random Scroll
  Runs an animation that scrolls cards at random.

Random Jump
  Runs an animation in which cards bounce up randomly from the bottom of the screen.

Random Trace
  Runs an animation that follows links at random.
