----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Settings Menu
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

GPT API Key
  Sets the API Key obtained from the OpenAI website in order to use GPT integration.

Auto Save Default
  Toggles the default automatic saving setting for newly created files.
  When enabled, new files will have automatic saving turned on from the start.

Auto Reload Default
  Toggles the default automatic reloading setting for newly created files.
  When enabled, new files will have automatic reloading turned on from the start.
